This paper is about improving the resilience of distributed training to worst-case, or Byzantine node failures, which is a common problem in large-scale machine learning tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
